<?xml version='1.0' standalone='yes'?>
<PLUGIN name="novidio-vgpu-driver" author="CaffeineCM" version="2026.03.03a" icon="microchip" launch="Settings/novidio-vgpu-driver" pluginURL="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/CaffeineCM/unraid-novidio-vgpu-driver/master/novidio-vgpu-driver.plg" min="6.11.5" support="https://www.lxg2016.com/">

<CHANGES>
##2026.03.03a
- Merge the 2026.03.01 through 2026.03.02 changes into a single stable release
- Add manual driver version selection plus validated local package upload support in the web UI
- Preserve selected, installed, and uploaded package versions in the dropdown when remote lookup fails
- Add persistent driver action logging and expose safer download-only and reboot-based install actions
- Stop automatic driver download and installation during plugin install, and apply prepared packages during boot
- Retry downloads cleanly, refresh package state correctly, and restore executable helper permissions
- Repair stale NVIDIA userspace symlinks after switching driver versions and stop reporting boot-time installs as successful on failure
- Show mdev devices and supported types directly from sysfs instead of requiring mdevctl

- 合并 2026.03.01 至 2026.03.02 期间的所有中间更新，整理为一个可用的稳定版本
- 在 Web UI 中新增手动驱动版本选择，并支持带校验的本地驱动包上传
- 当远程版本获取失败时，仍保留下拉框中的已选版本、已安装版本和本地导入版本
- 增加持久化驱动操作日志，并提供更安全的仅下载与重启安装操作
- 取消插件安装时自动下载和安装驱动，改为在启动阶段应用已准备好的驱动包
- 优化下载重试与包状态刷新逻辑，并恢复辅助脚本的可执行权限
- 修复切换驱动版本后 NVIDIA 用户态库符号链接残留问题，并避免在启动安装失败时误报成功
- 改为直接从 sysfs 读取 mdev 设备及其支持类型，不再依赖 mdevctl

##2025.01.22
- Fix naming issues and plugin page name
- improve plugin page layout

##2024.12.29
- Fixed typos in deployment
- Works with novidio build and deployment

###2023.05.01
- Fix Bug

###2023.05.01
